node.text:
🎥 @supercarblondie
These are my top 5 picks for the most amazing concept cars in the world! 🌟 2020 hasn't been the easiest year for travel but I'm so glad I still got to capture some of the coolest cars out this year! 😱😱 If you want to see the top 10 countdown for 2020 go check out my youtube channel and hit subscribe to see what's coming in 2021! xx Alex #supercarblondie  #conceptcars
